{
  "stem": "26585.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was tragic, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was one of our sadder moments, our liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sitting in the basement-- that thing was one of the very few times she-- she-- let us go in the basement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she sat next to us on the bench.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, a little boy came downstairs and cried the Americans are here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Looked at her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She sat like a statue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't dare breathing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, she got up, never looked at us, and started to walk up the steps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know why, but I saw something glittering-- it was the swastika.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, see this is a dumb thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should have saved it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I picked it up and it did me so good when I said, here, Frau so and so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She took it, never said a word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took over her room-- she with rooms-- we took those over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we sat, and finally Mother said, I guess we're going up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're free.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No emotion, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, we used to dream that we would scream and laugh and cry and dance-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Cold, total coldness on the inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Went upstairs, and Mother said, well, we may as well start cleaning up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, I want to wash myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And no, not yet, not yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the first time we saw the American, there was a courtyard, and we took water and our dirty clothes and just-- and all of a sudden, stop!",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Mm mm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was two American soldiers-- one tall, one not so tall-- filthy, dirty, with a drawn gun.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never seen a more beautiful sight in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
